originalText.text: Eugene has been cutting my hair for 16 & a half years and I wouldn't even think of going to anyone else. People frequently tell me that my hair looks good, even when I am long overdue for a trim, which I think is a sign of a good haircut. He's also very personable and reasonably priced.

originalText.text: I just so happened to be in the right place at the right time in the neighborhood, and asked on a whim if he had an opening and Sammy Pinkhasov took me in and gave me a quick and phenomenal cut! I was in desperate need and am very weird about my hair and going to new stylists. Within seconds my nerves were at ease and I was looking better. I only wish I could have him as my regular barber. If you can— get in with him! You won’t regret it!

originalText.text: I just went in for my first hair cut at Eugene's, and immediately told my roommates that this is where we'll be getting our hair cut from now on.  Eugene is talented, professional, and friendly--he gave me a great cut for a great price.
